{"timestamp":1774432507993,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"eae79627-fa8e-4e1c-b3b3-03434e5483bb","hook_event_type":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Read","tool_use_id":"toolu_01685xqHFXnhqtYGdV45MKWf","payload":{"session_id":"eae79627-fa8e-4e1c-b3b3-03434e5483bb","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-1aa6893e/eae79627-fa8e-4e1c-b3b3-03434e5483bb.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/1aa6893e","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PostToolUse","tool_name":"Read","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/1aa6893e/specs/issue-1aa6893e-adw-5015a2b4-sdlc_planner-plans-page-header-height.md"},"tool_response":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/1aa6893e/specs/issue-1aa6893e-adw-5015a2b4-sdlc_planner-plans-page-header-height.md","content":"# Plan: Update Plans Page Header to Be Taller\n\n## Task Description\nIncrease the height of the plans page collection header (`merch-card-collection-header.plans`) by overriding the header height CSS custom properties in the plans variant styles. No specific target height was provided, so apply a ~50% increase from the current default of 44px \u2192 66px.\n\n## Relevant Files\n\n- `web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js` \u2014 **edit**: add height overrides to the `merch-card-collection-header.plans` selector block (lines 256\u2013259) to increase filter and search heights.\n\n## Step by Step Tasks\n\n### 1. Read the current `merch-card-collection-header.plans` block\n- Open `web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js`\n- Locate the `merch-card-collection-header.plans` rule at ~line 256\n- Confirm existing properties: `--merch-card-collection-header-columns` and `--merch-card-collection-header-areas`\n\n### 2. Add height override variables\n- Inside `merch-card-collection-header.plans { ... }`, add:\n  ```css\n  --merch-card-collection-header-filter-height: 66px;\n  --merch-card-collection-header-search-min-height: 66px;\n  ```\n- These variables propagate automatically to the filter button (`#filter`), sort button (`#sort`, which inherits from filter height), and search input (`#search sp-search`) via the base component's CSS in `merch-card-collection.js`.\n\n### 3. Verify no layout breakage in the desktop override\n- The desktop media query at ~line 427 also has a `merch-card-collection-header.plans` block (overriding column/area layout only).\n- The height variables added in step 2 apply globally and will remain in effect at desktop unless overridden \u2014 this is the desired behavior.\n- No additional desktop override is needed unless a distinct desktop height is specified.\n\n### 4. Validate JS syntax\n- Run `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js`\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- `merch-card-collection-header.plans` renders with a taller header (~66px) compared to the default (44px).\n- The filter button, sort button, and search input inside the header are all taller.\n- No layout regression below the header (card grid, sidenav, content sections remain unaffected).\n- `node --check` passes with no syntax errors.\n\n## Validation Commands\n- `node --check web-components/src/variants/plans.css.js`\n","numLines":41,"startLine":1,"totalLines":41}},"tool_use_id":"toolu_01685xqHFXnhqtYGdV45MKWf"}}
